2. Difference between id and class attribute: The difference between them is that “id” is unique in a page and can only apply to at most one element, while “class” selector can apply to multiple elements.

3.There are many benefits of using CSS:
A) Smooth Website Speed
B) Easier to Maintain
C) Platforms Independence
D) Saves Times

